Class MovingObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.byu.cs.superasteroids.model.MovingObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Asteroid, Laser, Ship

    public class MovingObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Anything that moves needs to keep track of it's position and handle collision detection. Inheriting from this class lets it do just that.
